                            <comment id="14511050" author="jira-bot" created="Fri, 24 Apr 2015 13:35:51 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Commit 1675856 from &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/ViewProfile.jspa?name=kwall&quot; class=&quot;user-hover&quot; rel=&quot;kwall&quot;&gt;kwall&lt;/a&gt; in branch &apos;java/trunk&apos;&lt;br/&gt;
